name: Boogeyman - Card #09
description:
Boogeyman - Card #09
**********************************************************************
TYPE OF CARD: Plus
This card will add 50pts to your lowest level in the last round. 
You can only use 1 per fight. 
After being used the plus cards are burned. Only 1 plus card will exist.
**********************************************************************
1) Every copy you buy is an extra chance to win 1 ticket to the Maleducado World Cup.
2) Tickets will be raffled at the end of the 16 card drops.
3) *IMPORTANT* For more information on how to play check the rules on Google drive. Link on Twitter.
4) When Get a card, you will be part of the Twitter group. In case you don't have your account linked, send me a DM.
